# .cursorrules — Cursor Specific Notes

Core agent rules, conventions, and SDLC process are defined in `AGENTS.md`.

---

## Cursor Specifics

- Use a new Composer window to simulate subagents when needed.
- Background agents are in beta — use with caution.
- Cursor has strong filesystem and multi-file editing capabilities.

See `AGENTS.md` for:
- Session opening and closing protocol
- All commands
- Subagent system and triggers
- Core conventions